General.Name: TC Unterhaltungselektronik AG
General.Description: TC Unterhaltungselektronik AG offers software as a service in the fields of consumer verification, data protection, and financial services in Germany and internationally. It also develops secure data management strategies for its clients, as well as offers consulting services. The company was founded in 1995 and is based in Koblenz, Germany.
